{"tid":2428763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國2月製造業加快擴張   PMI升至55.1　創兩個月新高","createTime":"2021-03-01T19:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T05:34:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea03422f2a8217089f3fd2ad305ee05ce4fbc56","tid":2428763,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T19:32:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578180-20210301.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578180-20210301.htm&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt14aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=c1ed3ac4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578180-20210301.htm&h=947a2ffd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578180-20210301.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n英國2月製造業採購經理指數(PMI)終值升至55.1，高於1月終值的54.1，亦高於2月初值的54.9，指數升至兩個月高位。<br />\n<br />\n產出指數由50.7降至50.5，是去年5月以來最低，英國脫歐及疫情導致供應鏈中斷、成本上升，限制訂單溫和回升的能力。"},{"pid":"33fb461cedef6c944f2d978742340290e8fba5d7","tid":2428763,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:34:48.000Z","msg":"英國 GO GO GO <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}